/*
 * Stacking order
 *
 * USS has no `z-index` property (Unity 6.3 / 6.4; on the roadmap as "planning
 * beyond Unity 6.7 LTS"). Draw order is determined by sibling order in the tree
 * (a later sibling is drawn in front). Control it dynamically from C# with
 * `VisualElement.BringToFront()` / `SendToBack()` / `PlaceInFront(other)` /
 * `PlaceBehind(other)` rather than a `z-*` utility.
 */
